reviews.text:
Had to checkout Parlay TACOS & TEQUILA! The food, service and vibe is always amazing! 

- $4 Tacos 
- $5 Rey Supremo Blanco (shot or mixed drink) 
- $7 Rey...
The decor and layout was the most memorable aspect of my visit. I ordered the cauliflower steak which was served with a tasty Brussel sprouts and potato...
We were excited to hit Parlay as it was recommended by a girlfriend of mine. It was ok. We were quickly seated which was a bonus though had multiple servers...
